## Testing Workflow

1. **Register as Student** → Get auth token
2. **Browse Courses** → GET /courses
3. **View Course Details** → GET /courses/:id
4. **Enroll in Course** → POST /enrollments/enroll
5. **Track Progress** → POST /progress/track
6. **View Progress** → GET /progress/my-progress
7. **Generate Certificate** → POST /certificates/generate
8. **View Certificates** → GET /certificates/my-certificates

